snippet.textDisplay:
) I'm a Traditional Chinese Medicine doctor and I live in Sweden. In November 2019, a couple came to see me. The husband's name is Philip and he has problems with his gastrointestinal tract. His wife suffers from insomnia. After I examined them we chatted.

Philip is an IT engineer and told me he planned to travel to China on a business trip. At that time, there were media reports about a bubonic plague outbreak in Mongolia. I didn't know about the coronavirus, but I was worried that he might contract infectious diseases while in China. I asked, “Can you avoid going? When is your trip?” He replied that he was still waiting on instructions from his employers. I then told him that Shen Yun Performing Arts was performing in Stockholm from January 3-6, 2020, and I encouraged him to see the show. The couple was very excited said that they would take their entire family to see Shen Yun.

On January 3, 2020, Philip, his wife, son and daughter caught a train from Gothenburg to Stockholm to watch Shen Yun. They coincidentally sat in my row. After the show, Philip excitedly said, “I've never seen such a spectacular show! We'd love to see it again.”

In mid-February, 2020, Philip and his wife came to my clinic and told me about his trip to China.

He went to China for about two weeks in January. He went to several major cities including Beijing, Hangzhou, and Shanghai. Because of the epidemic he self-quarantined at home for 14 days when he returned. He did not have the coronavirus. He said joyfully, “I've been blessed!” His wife agreed. She said, “In the past it was a big thing to get anything done at home. After we watched Shen Yun, I don't know what happened but everything has gone smoothly. Now I even sleep much better!”

snippet.textDisplay: This is just my opinion.....Didn’t the President say a few weeks ago that we weren’t going to give or sell our extra equipment to other countries?  President trump should TRY to find and wear PPE and visit hospitals and ERs in our countries HOt Spots and in all the other states that either are now, or will become hot spots. He needs to see what our healthcare system employees and the public in general are dealing with. Can you imagine watching perhaps your loved ones body being loaded in the back of a freezer truck?  And what is going to happen to their bodies?  Has anyone said...maybe the families were informed....I hope to God the families!  It is none of our business, but I pray these families are not being held in limbo. Results for people tested are taking a very long time to get the results. This is one reason why some states are not showing true numbers. Why don’t we have every American tested?  NOW he is taking this seriously?  It was serious awhile ago!  Apparently the President and our other leaders of different departments DO NOT need to practice social distancing, you don’t need to run a temperature to have this terrible virus.  And virus’s do mutate!  It might be just me but it feels like I am being read a terrible children’s book every day with alternate endings!!!!!  Please don’t leave me nasty comments, parts of this is only what I have heard, read or think.....we are all entitled to our opinions if nothing else during this pandemic!

snippet.textDisplay:
Estimates broken down by age in the USA, April 1-June 1, 2020:

80-84: Infected: 30,000 Deaths: 5,400
70-79 Infected: 114,000 Deaths: 9,120
60-69 Infected: 175,000 Deaths: 7,000
50-59 Infected: 210,000 Deaths: 5,250
40-49 Infected: 197,000 Deaths: 3,000
20-39 Infected: 440,000 Deaths: 600

Totals: 1,166,000 Infected
Totals: 30,370 Deaths

This is based on the US population of 325,000,000 broken down into each age bracket multiplied by .5% (one half of one percent becoming Infected). I then broke those numbers down by the fatality rates given by the CDC for each age group.

The absolute devastation that this virus is capable of is sobering, and terrifying. May God have mercy on us.
